<t tx="T2198">System requirements for leo.py
------------------------------

leo.py requires Python 2.1 and tcl/tk 8.3 or above.

	Download Python from http://python.org/ 
	Download tcl/Tk from http://tcl.activestate.com/software/tcltk/

